1.
Download LibSVM:
www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~cjlin/cgi-bin/libsvm.cgi?+http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~cjlin/libsvm+tar.gz
2.
Extract the above and set the CLASSPATH from terminalas (unix based systems)
export CLASSPATH=/home/rahul/Downloads/libsvm-3.20/java/libsvm.jar
Here /home/rahul/Downloads/libsvm-3.20 was the path where I extracted the tar; Change this according to ur machine
3. 
Run weka.
>weka

